Gesture-Based Smart Door Unlock

Description
This project implements a gesture-based smart door unlock system using IoT technology. The system allows users to unlock their doors through specific hand gestures, enhancing security and convenience.

Features
Gesture recognition using [specific sensor/technology].
Secure unlocking mechanism.
User-friendly interface for setup and configuration.
Hardware Components
List of required components:
Microcontroller
Ultrasonic sensor
Servo motor
Power supply
Piezoelectric sensor
Buzzer
The software runs on Arduino IDE and uses Python for implementation.

